'''剑桥大学耶稣学院'''（{{lang-en|Jesus College, Cambridge}}）是[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]的一个[[剑桥大学学院列表|学院]]。其全名為圣母玛利亚、圣约翰福音和圣瑞迪南德学院，而其俗名源自耶穌禮拜堂（Jesus Chapel）。最近一任院長為工程學家伊恩·懷特（Ian White），2011年至2019年4月在任。

耶穌學院由約翰·阿爾科克（John Alcock）於1496年創立，座落於之[[本笃会|本笃会]]幼兒院原址。其徽章上的[[公雞|公雞]]圖案亦源自阿爾科克之姓氏<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.britannica.com/biography/John-Alcock|title=John Alcock {{!}} English bishop and statesman|accessdate=2019-05-11|work=Encyclopedia Britannica|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122120437/https://www.britannica.com/biography/John-Alcock|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

總共有3位[[諾貝爾獎|諾貝爾獎]]得主來自耶穌學院<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213113454/http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/nobel-laureates/|title=Nobel Laureates {{!}} Jesus College Cambridge|accessdate=2019-05-10|date=2016-02-13|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>，2位院士被任命為[[国际法院|國際法庭]]成員<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduates/subject-information/law/judges/|title=Judges {{!}} Jesus College Cambridge|accessdate=2019-05-10|author=|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927011752/http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduates/subject-information/law/judges/|archivedate=2015-09-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。校友在社會各界均有傑出表現。耶穌學院是為劍橋第三富有的學院<ref>http://archive.varsity.co.uk/647.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://archive.varsity.co.uk/647.pdf |date=20160826092226 }} Old,Rich, Landed and Loaded. Varsity, 17th November 2006, P.6</ref>，總資產達到2.43億英鎊。耶穌學院因其佔地廣闊而廣為人知。

==歷史==
[[File:Jesus_College,_Cambridge_by_Loggan_1690_-_Folger_046539W5.jpg|left]]
书院于一四九六年成立，建筑物均沿襲自于十二世纪初成立的圣玛丽和圣拉德贡修道院；书院之建築物是剑桥最古老的大学建筑，至今仍在使用<ref name=":1" />，其落成的時間比书院成立和剑桥大学成立分別早三百五十年和半个世纪。

本笃会修院解散後，礼拜堂和附属于它的回廊都納入耶穌學院範圍之中；修女们的食堂成了学院的礼堂；以往院长的住处成為院长的住处<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/about-us/history/1496-1559|title=1496 to 1559|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150448/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/about-us/history/1496-1559|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这组建筑至今仍是学院的核心，其独特的修道院建筑风格，使其有别于其他剑桥学院。不久，耶穌學院擁有屬於自己的图书馆，阿尔科克大幅修改小教堂，教堂規模也隨之為縮小。建校时，全學院有一位教授、六位研究员和六位學生<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Biographical Dictionary, Or, Complete Historical Library: Containing the Lives of the Most Celebrated Personages of Great Britain and Ireland, Whether Admirals, Generals, Poets, Statesmen, Philosophers, Or Divines : a Work Replete with Instruction and Entertainment|last=Society of gentlemen|first=|publisher=F. Newbery|year=1780|isbn=|location=|pages=30|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8jtQAQAAIAAJ|access-date=2019-05-11|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110346/https://books.google.com/books?id=8jtQAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1976年耶穌學院開始招收女性。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/about-us/history/women-jesus-college|title=Women at Jesus College|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110354/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/about-us/history/women-jesus-college|dead-url=no}}</ref><br />

==學術概況==
儘管耶穌學院學生大多修讀[[工程学|工程]]、[[医学|醫學]]、[[法学院|法律]]、[[自然科学|自然科学]]、[[数学|数学]]、[[经济|经济]]、[[历史|历史]]、[[語言|語言]]、以及[[人文学科|人文]][[政治|政治]]科學，耶穌學院仍然接受修讀所有科目的[[高等教育|本科生]]和[[研究生|研究生]]入讀<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduates/subject-information/|title=Subject information - Jesus College Cambridge|accessdate=2016-03-13|author=|date=|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315190415/http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/admissions/undergraduates/subject-information/|archivedate=2016-03-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。學院為學生提供多樣的[[獎學金|獎學金]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/graduate/finance-funding-scholarships-and-bursaries|title=Finance, funding, scholarships, and bursaries|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609181534/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/graduate/finance-funding-scholarships-and-bursaries|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该学院在非正式、根据本科生成绩為學院排名次的[[汤普金斯排行榜|汤普金斯排行榜]]中一直名列前茅<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sohu.com/a/293008089_490063|title=最新牛津剑桥学院排名来啦，最好的是哪个？_诺林顿|accessdate=2019-05-11|work=www.sohu.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804223411/https://www.sohu.com/a/293008089_490063|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==建筑物==
===大門===
[[File:Jesus_College,_Cambridge_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1062931.jpg|thumb]]

耶稣学院的大門是一个有围墙的通道，被称为「烟囱」<ref>{{Cite book|title=Cambridge|last=Hall|first=Michael|publisher=Pevensey Press|year=1993|isbn=9780907115632|location=|pages=41}}</ref>（Chimney）。这个詞語来源于中古法语单词chemin，表示「路径」或「方式」。大門直通守門人之住處，然后进入第一個庭院<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/location-and-virtual-tour|title=Location and virtual tour|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110445/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/location-and-virtual-tour|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了回廊以外，学院的所有庭院至少有一面是开放的。

===图书馆===
====五百周年图书馆====
五百年图书馆是耶稣学院的主要图书馆，每天24小时开放<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/quincentenary-library|title=Quincentenary Library|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150535/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/quincentenary-library|dead-url=no}}</ref>。图书馆由埃尔德里德·埃文斯（Eldred Evans）和大卫·沙莱夫（David Shalev）设计，以纪念该学院500周年校慶<ref name="#1"/>。图书馆竣工后不久，在2000年建造了一座新的宿舍楼<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/|title=History (1945-)|accessdate=2014-02-18|author=|date=April 2011|publisher=Jesus College, Cambridge|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201033055/http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/|archivedate=2014-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。五百周年图书馆收納了大量法律典籍，它們被安置在一楼的法律图书馆。

====旧图书馆====
旧图书馆一直使用到1912年。其館藏擁有超过9,000本书籍<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/old-library|title=Old Library|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110445/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/old-library|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并開放予研究人员预约。旧图书馆館藏包括马尔萨斯藏品集<ref name=":0" />，是該校校友马尔萨斯的家族藏品。

====教堂和唱诗班====
[[File:The_Chapel,_Jesus_College,_Cambridge_-_geograph.org.uk_-_1057669.jpg|thumb]]
学院教堂始建于1157年，直到1245年才完工<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/history-chapel|title=History of the Chapel, The Convent Church (12th to 14th centuries)|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150546/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/history-chapel|dead-url=no}}</ref>，被认为是剑桥仍在使用的最古老的大学建筑。 最初是圣玛丽和圣拉德贡的本笃会修道院，后来被约翰·阿尔科克主教解散<ref name=":1" />。<br/>教堂的原始结构是十字形的，中殿被南北走廊貫通。 一个高而倾斜的屋顶被钟楼和尖塔所覆盖；但屋頂於1277年倒塌。这个小礼拜堂也被用作圣拉德贡的教区教堂。教堂在1313年和1376年两次遭遇大火<ref name=":1" />。

当学院在15世纪接管整個教區时，教区以学院的名字重新命名为耶稣教区，教堂墓地仍然運作。 然而耶稣教区的存在十分短暂，因为到了16世纪中叶，耶稣教区被并入万圣堂教區。阿尔科克為教堂作出了重大改建，将剑桥最大的教堂改建为学院小礼拜堂，供該学院学者使用<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/history-chapel|title=History of the Chapel, The College Chapel (late 15th to early 16th centuries)|accessdate=2019-05-11|author=|date=|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150546/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/history-chapel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原来的中殿成為学院的房间所和教授住宿。

在学期中，每天都会举行誦經和唱頌彌撒。唱頌黃昏祈禱每周进行四次（星期二，星期四，星期六和星期日），星期日早晨舉行圣餐禮。 每学期还有两次晚禱，以及圣日弥撒<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/chapel-services-events-and-hire|title=Chapel services, events, and hire|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211110443/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/chapel-and-choir/about-chapel/chapel-services-events-and-hire|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

====大學校園====
耶稣学院擁有一片偌大的运动场地。學院運動場地包含足球、橄榄球、板球、网球、壁球、篮球和曲棍球场。 耶稣学院的船屋距學院主建築群只有400码远<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/undergraduatehandbook.pdf|title=Jesus College Undergraduate Handbook|accessdate=2016-03-27|author=|date=|publisher=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411094737/http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/undergraduatehandbook.pdf|archivedate=2016-04-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

大学校園內還有一条自然徑，其建築灵感来自[[塞缪尔·泰勒·柯勒律治|塞缪尔·泰勒·柯勒律治]]在学生时代创作的诗歌<ref>[http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/pen-portraits/samuel-taylor-coleridge/ http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/pen-portraits/samuel-taylor-coleridge/;] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/about-jesus-college/history/pen-portraits/samuel-taylor-coleridge/ |date=20160430204654 }} http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/undergraduatehandbook.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/undergraduatehandbook.pdf |date=20160411094737 }}</ref>。

耶稣学院是少数几所允许任何人在院子的草坪上散步的学院之一，第一院、回廊院和故修道院已故修女墓地除外<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/conferences/contact-us/information|title=Information|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813025020/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/conferences/contact-us/information|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 与其他剑桥大学一样，这项特权只有在复活节期间才会延伸至學院所有地方。

==学生生活==
=== 学生社团 ===
虽然耶稣学院歷史悠久，但它以轻松随意的气氛而著称。耶稣学院学生会（JSCU）和耶稣学院研究生会（MCR）都相當活跃<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/arts-music-sports-and-societies/societies-and-social|title=Societies and social|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150711/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/arts-music-sports-and-societies/societies-and-social|dead-url=no}}</ref>。学生会每年都會组织各种各样的社会、文化、福利和体育活动<ref name=":2" />。 其中约翰休斯艺术节于2014年由学院学生创办，以纪念已故教堂主任约翰·休斯（John Hughes）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thetab.com/uk/cambridge/2015/01/23/preview-the-john-hughes-arts-festival-44984|title=PREVIEW: The John Hughes Arts Festival|accessdate=2019-05-11|date=2015-01-23|work=University of Cambridge|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150719/https://thetab.com/uk/cambridge/2015/01/23/preview-the-john-hughes-arts-festival-44984|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

耶稣学院每年举办一次五月舞会（May Ball）。音乐家詹姆斯·贝（James Bay）亦曾在舞会上表演<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thetab.com/uk/cambridge/2015/06/21/review-jesus-may-ball-55162|title=REVIEW: Jesus May Ball|accessdate=2019-05-11|date=2015-06-20|work=University of Cambridge|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150639/https://thetab.com/uk/cambridge/2015/06/21/review-jesus-may-ball-55162|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，耶稣学院提供许多运动项目，包括划船、足球、橄榄球、曲棍球、网球、壁球和篮球<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/arts-music-sports-and-societies/sports|title=Sports|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150722/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/arts-music-sports-and-societies/sports|dead-url=no}}</ref>。学院通常在每项运动中派出若干队伍，以划艇俱乐部表現最為出色，男子八人划艇队在五月颠簸赛中，排名从未跌至第12位以下。 划艇俱乐部每年举办费尔贝恩杯赛事<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesusboatclub.co.uk/fairbairns|title=Jesus College Boat Club {{!}} The Fairbairn Cup|accessdate=2019-05-11|work=Jesus College Boat Club {{!}} Home|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150647/https://www.jesusboatclub.co.uk/fairbairns|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 膳食 ===
学院的主餐厅每周有五个為學生晚上提供三道菜的正式晚餐。学院的所有成员都穿礼服<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/formal-hall|title=Formal Hall|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150654/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/formal-hall|dead-url=no}}</ref>。每个星期三，研究生堂都会为研究生们准备四道菜的晚餐<ref name=":3" />。与大多数传统的牛津剑桥大学不同，这所大学允许研究生在周二的高桌晚宴上用餐<ref name=":3" />。

学院咖啡廳亦提供午餐和晚餐，<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/cafeteria|title=Cafeteria|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150658/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/cafeteria|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在星期六上午提供[[早午餐|早午餐]]<ref name=":4" />，以及在星期日提供烤肉午餐<ref name=":4" />。学院还有一个很受欢迎的学生酒吧叫做JBar，出售各种各样的饮料，包括 JPA (耶稣淡啤酒)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/bar|title=The Roost Bar|accessdate=2019-05-11|last=College|first=Jesus|work=Jesus College University of Cambridge|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219150706/https://www.jesus.cam.ac.uk/college/life-jesus/food-and-drink/bar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
